import React from 'react'
import Hero from './Hero'
import Features from './Features'
import FooterCopyright from './FooterCopyright'

const HomePage = () => {
  return (
    <>
        <Hero></Hero>
        <Features></Features>
        <FooterCopyright></FooterCopyright>
    </>
  )
}

export default HomePage
